Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.search

Class StructTypePropertyValue

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.search.PropertyValue
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.search.StructTypePropertyValue
public class StructTypePropertyValue extends PropertyValue
StructTypePropertyValue supports the value part of property that is defined as a complex structure. It manages a list of properties that cover the fields in the structure.
